name: NMLS registry information; challenge process
text: §454F-11  NMLS registry information; challenge process.  The commissioner shall establish a process by rule pursuant to chapter 91 whereby a licensee may challenge information entered into NMLS by the commissioner. [L Sp 2009, c 32, pt of §2; am L 2010, c 84, §18; am L 2013, c 168, §14]
